+Say you have a file called ``my_file.py``. ``import-self`` would be raised on the following code::
+
+
+    from my_file import a_function  # [import-self]
+
+    def a_function():
+        pass
+
+The solution would be to remove the import::
+
+    def a_function():
+        pass
